## 📚 What is Libft? | ስለ Libft

Libft is the very first project in the 42 School curriculum. The goal is to **recreate several standard C library functions** from scratch — without using any of the built-in C library functions (except `write`, `malloc`, and `free` in some cases).

Libft በ 42 ትምህርት መነሻ ፕሮጀክት ነው። ከ C ቋንቋ ውስጥ የተለመዱ ፋንክሽኖችን በእራሳችን እንድንፃፍ ያስገደደና በስራ ይወቃል።

### This project helps understand:
- 🧠 Memory manipulation (ማስታወሻን መቆጣጠር)
- 🧵 String operations (የየሴት ሐረጎች ስራዎች)
- 🔣 Character checks (የቁምፊ ምርመራ)
- 🌿 Linked list data structures (ተያያዥ ዝርዝር)
- ⚙️ How the C Standard Library works under the hood (የ C መደበኛ መጻሕፍት የውስጥ አሰራር)

👉 **Libft is the foundation for almost every future project at 42.**

