## 🚀 Project Structure | የፕሮጀክቱ መዋቅር

### Part 1 – Libc Functions | የመደበኛው ፋንክሽኖች መቅደም

```c
ft_memset, ft_bzero, ft_memcpy, ft_memmove  
ft_strlcpy, ft_strlcat, ft_strlen, ft_strchr, ft_strrchr  
ft_strncmp, ft_memchr, ft_memcmp, ft_strnstr  
ft_atoi, ft_isalpha, ft_isdigit, ft_isalnum, ft_isascii, ft_isprint  
ft_toupper, ft_tolower  
ft_calloc, ft_strdup

Part 2 – Additional Functions | ተጨማሪ ስራዎች


ft_substr, ft_strjoin, ft_strtrim  
ft_split, ft_itoa, ft_strmapi, ft_striteri  
ft_putchar_fd, ft_putstr_fd, ft_putendl_fd, ft_putnbr_fd

Bonus Part – Linked Lists | ቦነስ: ሊንክ ዝርዝሮች

ft_lstnew, ft_lstadd_front, ft_lstsize, ft_lstlast  
ft_lstadd_back, ft_lstdelone, ft_lstclear, ft_lstiter, ft_lstmap


🛠️ How to Compile | እንዴት እንደሚሰራ

make        # libft.a እንዲሰራ  
make clean  # የ .o ፋይሎችን ማጥፋት  
make fclean # ሁሉንም ፋይል ማጥፋት  
make re     # ነጠላ ማቀናበሪያ ከመጀመሪያ



Example of using Libft in your program:


#include "libft.h"

int main(void)
{
    ft_putstr_fd("Hello Libft!\n", 1);
    return (0);
}


📌 Final Notes | መጨረሻ ማስታወሻ

This project is part of the 42 School Curriculum. Please do not copy others' code — it’s better to struggle and learn step by step.
